"在定义用户模型的外键或多对多关系时，应使用 :setting:`AUTH_USER_MODEL` 配置指"
"定自定义模型。例如："

msgid ""
"When connecting to signals sent by the user model, you should specify the "
"custom model using the :setting:`AUTH_USER_MODEL` setting. For example::"
