"models.Field.blank` 为 ``False`` 或未定义的任何字段，并可能包括你希望在交互式"
"创建用户时提示的其他字段。``REQUIRED_FIELDS`` 在 Django 的其他部分没有效果，"
"比如在管理中创建用户。"

msgid ""
":attr:`REQUIRED_FIELDS` now supports :class:`~django.db.models."
"ManyToManyField`\\s without a custom through model. Since there is no way to "
"pass model instances during the :djadmin:`createsuperuser` prompt, expect "
"the user to enter IDs of existing instances of the class to which the model "
"is related."
msgstr ""
":attr:`REQUIRED_FIELDS` 现在支持 :class:`~django.db.models.ManyToManyField`，"
"不需要自定义的中间模型。由于在 :djadmin:`createsuperuser` 提示中没有办法传递"
"模型实例，所以希望用户输入模型相关的类的现有实例的 ID。"

