msgstr "避免过度复杂的事情"

msgid ""
"Generally you can use :class:`~django.views.generic.base."
"TemplateResponseMixin` and :class:`~django.views.generic.detail."
"SingleObjectMixin` when you need their functionality. As shown above, with a "
