"Creates a new savepoint. This marks a point in the transaction that is known "
"to be in a \"good\" state. Returns the savepoint ID (``sid``)."
msgstr ""
"创建新的保存点。这标志着事务中已知处于“良好”状态的一个点。返回保存点ID "
"(``sid``) 。"

msgid ""
